@startuml seq_login
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Customer
participant "React\n/login" as UI
participant "AuthController" as Ctrl
participant "AuthService" as Svc
database "SQL Server" as DB

Customer -> UI : email + password
UI -> Ctrl : POST /api/auth/login
Ctrl -> Svc : LoginAsync
Svc -> DB : read User + RolePermissions
Svc -> Svc : BCrypt verify\ncheck IsLocked / IsActive
Svc --> Ctrl : JWT + user + permissions
Ctrl --> UI : 200 accessToken
UI --> Customer : navigate ROLE_LANDING
@enduml
